(39, 'A Weighted Fuzzy Reasoning Process Neural Network and its Application', 'LIU Xian-de ,LI Huan', 'According to dynamic information processing\nproblems concerning process fuzzy information or domain\nrules, this paper presents a weighted fuzzy reasoning\nprocess neuron and a weighted fuzzy reasoning process\nneural network model. The Weighted Fuzzy Reasoning\nprocess neuron uses dynamic information processing\nmethods of fuzzy process reasoning rules and numerical\nprocess neuron in combination, and implements adaptive\nfuzzy reasoning to the process quantitative and qualitative\nmixed information with learning mechanism of process\nneuron.The fuzzy reasoning process neural network that\nmakes up of weighted fuzzy reasoning process neuron and\nother types of neurons according to certain information\ntransmission and fuzzy reasoning rules, extends fuzzy\nfunction mapping relation of traditional fuzzy neural\nnetworks to mapping relation of fuzzy functional, which\nimproves comprehensive information treatment capacity\nfor various kinds of process information. A weighted fuzzy\nreasoning process neural network model and its learning\nalgorithm have been given. Practical application results\nproved the effectiveness of the model and the algorithm.', 'a:79:{i:1;s:1:"*";i:4;s:6:"jurnal";i:8;s:1:"-";i:9;s:5:"judul";i:10;d:0.29999999999999999;i:11;s:2:"*j";i:12;s:6:"juduls";i:13;s:2:"-j";i:14;d:0.10000000000000001;i:15;s:7:"network";i:16;s:2:"-j";i:17;d:0.10000000000000001;i:18;s:2:"it";i:19;s:2:"-j";i:20;d:0.10000000000000001;i:21;s:6:"applic";i:22;s:2:"-j";i:23;d:0.10000000000000001;i:24;s:6:"neural";i:25;s:2:"-j";i:26;d:0.10000000000000001;i:27;s:7:"process";i:28;s:2:"-j";i:29;d:0.10000000000000001;i:30;s:5:"fuzzi";i:31;s:2:"-j";i:32;d:0.10000000000000001;i:33;s:6:"reason";i:34;s:2:"-j";i:35;d:0.10000000000000001;i:36;s:6:"weight";i:37;s:1:"#";i:38;s:1:"-";i:39;s:7:"keyword";i:40;d:0.40000000000000002;i:41;s:2:"*k";i:42;s:8:"keywords";i:43;s:2:"-k";i:44;d:0.2999999