(40, 'Evaluation of Technical Innovation Ability Based on Fuzzy TOPSIS Method', 'Shunkun Yu, Yufeng Shi', 'Under the market economy condition , enterprises\nexistence and development depends on competitive\nadvantage, however technical innovation ability is the\nfundamental supports and decisive factors of competitive\nadvantage, the modern enterprises'' existence and\ndevelopment depend on the knowledge and technologys\ninnovation and application more than before. But\npromoting technological innovation must establish on the\nbasis of accurate analysis and evaluation for\ntechnological innovation capability, the evaluation of\ntechnological innovation capability seems particularly\nimportant. In this paper , based on the mark system of\nenterprise technical innovation and fuzzy set theory,\naccording to the established evaluation index system of\ntechnical innovation ability, we use the fuzzy TOPSIS\nmethod to evaluate enterprises technical innovation\nability, some valuable information is acquired.', 'a:73:{i:1;s:1:"*";i:4;s:6:"jurnal";i:8;s:1:"-";i:9;s:5:"judul";i:10;d:0.29999999999999999;i:11;s:2:"*j";i:12;s:6:"juduls";i:13;s:2:"-j";i:14;d:0.10000000000000001;i:15;s:5:"fuzzi";i:16;s:2:"-j";i:17;d:0.10000000000000001;i:18;s:5:"topsi";i:19;s:2:"-j";i:20;d:0.10000000000000001;i:21;s:6:"method";i:22;s:2:"-j";i:23;d:0.10000000000000001;i:24;s:4:"base";i:25;s:2:"-j";i:26;d:0.10000000000000001;i:27;s:4:"abil";i:28;s:2:"-j";i:29;d:0.10000000000000001;i:30;s:7:"technic";i:31;s:2:"-j";i:32;d:0.10000000000000001;i:33;s:5:"innov";i:34;s:2:"-j";i:35;d:0.10000000000000001;i:36;s:5:"evalu";i:37;s:1:"#";i:38;s:1:"-";i:39;s:7:"keyword";i:40;d:0.40000000000000002;i:41;s:2:"*k";i:42;s:8:"keywords";i:43;s:2:"-k";i:44;d:0.40000000000000002;i:45;s:5:"innov";i:46;s:2:"-k";i:47;d:0.29999999999999999;i:48;s:5:"fuzzi";i:49;s:2:"-k";i:50;d:0.20000000000000001;i:51;s:7:"technic";i:52;s:2:"-k";i:53;d:0.10000000000000001;i:54;s:5:"evalu";i:55;s:1:"#";i:56;s:1:"-";i:57;s:7:"penulis";i:58;d:0.